<p>Hello <%=@employee.name%>,</p>

<p>This email is to inform you that the <strong><%= @meeting.title %></strong> meeting has changed. The meeting details are now as follows:
  <ul>
    <li>Title: <%= @meeting.title %> </li>
    <li>Location: <%= @meeting.location %> </li>
    <li>Start Time: <%= @meeting.start_time %> </li>
    <li>End Time: <%= @meeting.end_time %> </li>
    <li>Room: <%= @meeting.room.name %> (<%= @meeting.room.room_number %>) </li>
    <li>Attendees:
      <ol><% @meeting.employees.each do |employee| %>
        <li><%= employee.name %></li>
      <% end %>
      </ol>
    </li>
  </ul>
</p>
<p>Please be sure to arrive on time. Thank you.</p>

<p>Sincerely,</p>
<p><%= @meeting.employee.company.name %> Management</p>
